videos.description: UConn's Megan Walker finds Anna Makurat cutting to the hoop and fires a quick pass for an early Connecticut bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Makurat capitalizes on backdoor cut with nice lefty finish) 2020/3/2

videos.headline: Makurat capitalizes on backdoor cut with nice lefty finish

videos.description: The Huskies execute a perfect bucket in transition, showing off their impressive ball movement before Aubrey  Griffin lays it in to force a South Florida timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Griffin's layup caps UConn's 12-0 run vs. South Florida) 2020/3/2

videos.headline: Griffin's layup caps UConn's 12-0 run vs. South Florida

videos.description: Christyn Williams doesn't let South Florida's defense get in her way as she rushes to the hoop for two.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Williams steps over her defender for two) 2020/3/2
